title: #92Noon!  9am Hour 7/21 - We Made It/Vikes Bites/Kyndra De St Aubin
description: Nordo celeberates making it through the "worst sports day of the year", discusses why Kyle Rudolph could have a career resurgence in Tampa Bay, plus Kyndra De St Aubin calls in to talk about last night's exciting Loons win over Everton FC.
